@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_igvbdc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.97) + wp.exp(v2 + 0.88)) / ((v0 + 0.29 / v2 + 0.29) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.84)))
    v1 = v0
    v0 = 0.35
    data[tid] = v0
